===================================
ESCAPE FROM HANGAR 10 README
===================================

Escape From Hangar 10 v1.1

===================================
Installation
===================================

Extract anywhere and run setup.exe

===================================
Controls
===================================

Windows

Left Arrow/A - Move Left
Right Arrow/D - Move Right
Q/E - Change Weapon
Mouse - Aim/Navigate Menu
R - Reload
Esc - Pause/Exit Game

